---
// Sekcja Rozwiązanie - dopiero teraz oferta
---

<section id="dla-placowek" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Jak możemy pomóc
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Karta 1: Szkolenia -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Szkolenia
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Praktyczne warsztaty oparte na realnych przypadkach klinicznych, prowadzone przez aktywnych praktyków medycznych.
        </p>
        <a href="#szkolenia-details" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Dowiedz się więcej
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Karta 2: Konsultacje indywidualne -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Konsultacje indywidualne
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Wsparcie 1:1 dostosowane do Twoich potrzeb – rozwijaj kompetencje, rozwiązuj problemy, planuj rozwój kariery.
        </p>
        <a href="#konsultacje" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Dowiedz się więcej
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Karta 3: Wdrożenia w placówkach -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Wdrożenia w placówkach
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Kompleksowe wsparcie: budowanie procesów, rekrutacja personelu, organizacja pracy zespołu.
        </p>
        <a href="#wdrozenia" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Dowiedz się więcej
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
